node.text: Has this been made already? I haven’t seen it but the internet exists so I imagine it’s been made. I’m gonna have some kid in my DM like “MY FRIEND JOEY MADE THIS IN 1997.” Then I gotta bang Joey’s mom. The circle of life. I have no idea where I’m going with this GOOD MORNING EVERYONE SAY IT BACK

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kevin Flynn in West Palm Beach, Florida with @therecoveringproblemchild. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'Y me. You came back'.

node.text: I just got home from a 39 day vacation. Holy shit I’m so happy to be back at my house for longer than 3 days. Im so fucking sick of being on vacation. SHOUTOUT TO THE FRIENDS I MET ALONG THE WAY THO. I’m seriously going to sleep for like a week straight then not leaving my house for a month. Then maybe pee on myself a little. Or wait, I have to go to Miami in like a week and then Orlando the week after OH GOD DAMN IT (credit @therecoveringproblemchild )
